---
// Tools Section Component
---

<section id="tools" class="py-16 bg-gray-50">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4">Our Financial Technology Stack</h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        We leverage industry-leading financial tools and technologies to deliver accurate, efficient, and scalable solutions for your business.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <!-- Tool Card 1 -->
      <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md transition-transform hover:scale-105">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center h-16 w-16 rounded-full bg-primary-100 mx-auto mb-4">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-8 w-8 text-primary-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 7h6m0 10v-3m-3 3h.01M9 17h.01M9 14h.01M12 14h.01M15 11h.01M12 11h.01M9 11h.01M7 21h10a2 2 0 002-2V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v14a2 2 0 002 2z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-center mb-2">QuickBooks Online</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 text-center">
          Industry-standard accounting software for accurate financial tracking, reporting, and tax preparation.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Tool Card 2 -->
      <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md transition-transform hover:scale-105">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center h-16 w-16 rounded-full bg-primary-100 mx-auto mb-4">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-8 w-8 text-primary-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-center mb-2">Tableau</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 text-center">
          Advanced data visualization platform for creating interactive financial dashboards and business intelligence.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Tool Card 3 -->
      <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md transition-transform hover:scale-105">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center h-16 w-16 rounded-full bg-primary-100 mx-auto mb-4">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-8 w-8 text-primary-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8c-1.657 0-3 .895-3 2s1.343 2 3 2 3 .895 3 2-1.343 2-3 2m0-8c1.11 0 2.08.402 2.599 1M12 8V7m0 1v8m0 0v1m0-1c-1.11 0-2.08-.402-2.599-1M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-center mb-2">Xero</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 text-center">
          Cloud-based accounting software for streamlined invoicing, expense tracking, and financial management.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Tool Card 4 -->
      <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md transition-transform hover:scale-105">
